Package com.argox.sdk.barcodeprinter.emulation.pplz

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PPLZ
    This class is the subject of PPLZ emulator, including all different functions of PPLZ emulator.
    PPLZ_BarcodeUtil
    This class provides methods for barcode related programs of the PPLZ emulator.
    PPLZ_FormatUtil
    This class provides the method of PPLZ emulator 'Format' related procedures.
    PPLZ_GraphicsUtil
    This class provides methods for drawing related programs of the PPLZ emulator.
    PPLZ_InternalFun  
    PPLZ_IOUtil
    This class provides the method of PPLZ emulator printer output/input related procedures.
    PPLZ_SetUtil
    This class provides methods for setting programs related to the printer parameters of the PPLZ emulator.
    PPLZ_TextUtil
    This class provides methods for text-related programs of the PPLZ emulator.

    PPLZBarCodeType

    This enumeration is used to set the unit of measure for the printer.
